# IntradayScreener Bot + Web UI

A complete automated trading system with a Python/FastAPI backend and a Next.js 14 frontend.

## Features implemented

## 1. Safety First üõ°Ô∏è
- **Trading Guard**: Enforces `9:30 AM` start time to avoid initial volatility.
- **Rate Limit Protection**: Throttles requests (5/sec) and implements smart retry logic for `AB2001` errors.
- **Error Handling**: Converts cryptic codes (e.g., `AG8001`) into human-readable logs ("Invalid Token").

## 2. Real-Time Core ‚ö°
- **WebSocket Orders**: Instant fill notifications via [smart_websocket.py](file:///C:/Users/Ashbin/.gemini/antigravity/brain/2df2ed12-f98d-4c89-bf98-dea5fc2acbc3/smart_websocket.py).
- **Postback**: Backup HTTPS webhook at `/webhook/angel-one`.
- **Persistence Layer**: [state_manager.py](file:///C:/Users/Ashbin/.gemini/antigravity/brain/2df2ed12-f98d-4c89-bf98-dea5fc2acbc3/state_manager.py) saves `BOT_STATE` to disk ([bot_state.json](file:///C:/Users/Ashbin/.gemini/antigravity/brain/2df2ed12-f98d-4c89-bf98-dea5fc2acbc3/bot_state.json)) periodically and on every critical update. Prevents data loss during restarts.
- **Self-Healing Reconciliation**: On startup and every minute, the bot syncs with Angel One. It imports "Orphan" trades (manual/external buys) and auto-manages them with your default SL/Target settings!
- **Late Entry Protection**: The Strategy now rejects buy signals if the price is > 1.5% away from the EMA 20, preventing "FOMO" entries at the top.

## 4. Enhanced Exit Strategy üìâ
- **Breakeven Lock (+1R)**: If a trade moves +1R (Risk) in profit, the SL is automatically moved to Entry. Zero risk.
- **Strict Technical Exit**: Exits only on **Confirmed Candle Close** (15-min) below EMA20 AND VWAP. Prevents whipsaws.
- **Time-Based Exit**: Automatically closes stagnant trades (>60 mins with <0.5% profit) to free up capital.
- **Priority Logic**: Hard SL > Breakeven > Tech Exit > Time Exit.

